{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/New_Piskel__4_.png?t=1730397951\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*THIS GAME IS NO LONGER SUPPORTED, unfortunately this game did not receive the funding we needed to continue working on it and bring it to the quality we wanted. We appreciate everyone who supported this project and we're still proud of our first commercial release. BirdsBorough has been made free for anyone who enjoys the game or is curious to continue playing.*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After mysterious events a run-down potion shop has found it's way into your possession! The people of BirdsBorough have many unique problems for you to solve but you can create just as many unique potions brewed with various properties and powers. As you grow close to the people of BirdsBorough you may learn more secrets of this mysterious town you find yourself.... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Combine 27 unique potion effects </strong>using a colour mixing alchemy system. All effects have can be combined by matching their effect colours in the cauldron and mixing them all together! All potions drastically effect those who drink them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__6_.gif?t=1730397951\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__7_.gif?t=1730397951\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Solve NPCs unique problems</strong>, all NPCs have procedurally generated dialogue, so they'll always have something unique to say and unique problems to solve! It's up to you to figure out which potion would best help each NPC. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__8_.gif?t=1730397951\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build your own potion store</strong> with various decorations and structures, in whatever way you want! As you collect funds from potion sales you'll be able to build you're own store in a large plot of land in the town, however you see fit, will you create an ominous monolith? A simple market stall? Or something else entirely! It's all up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__5_.gif?t=1730397951\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Grow and harvest multiple unique plants</strong>, from elder trees to death blooms, all of which will affect your potions in different ways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/plamts.png?t=1730397951\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/New_Piskel__4_.png?t=1730397951\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730397951","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/page.bg.jpg?t=1730397951","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730397951","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730397951","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"NPC dialogue contains strong language/mature themes"},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\"